					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The Super NES and Sega Genesis were capable of interlacing, but few games used interlaced modes because they would need double the CHR memory to get an equivalent picture.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
